[gd_scene format=3 uid="uid://b1lampmsterenc01"]

; Five slots laid out horizontally: Lampmaster in the middle, 4 lamp slots
; flanking. Coordinate space matches what NCombatRoom expects (it offsets the
; Control by -(960, 540), so y=740 puts creatures at vanilla enemy height and
; x>960 keeps them on the enemy side of the screen).

